title: The Journal of Sir Walter Scott; From the Original Manuscript at Abbotsford
author: Scott, Walter
snippet: _July_ 5.--Saturday, corrected proofs and wrought hard. Went out todinner at Oxenfoord Castle, and returned in the company of Lord Alloway,Chief Baron, Clerk, etc., and Mr. Bouverie, the English Commissioner.
